DataElement.preferredDefinition: A data visualization technique which reduces the dimensions of data through the use of self-organizing neural networks. SOMs scale well to large data sets, can identify local clusters in the data and organize them globally, and proceed in an unsupervised fashion.:Something distinguishable as an identifiable class based on common qualities._The words or language units by which a thing is known._Generic value domain for a java datatype that is an array of strings.
